-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/merchants-wicked-unless-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":12638,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trade: Merchants with the wicked, unless they fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah ibn Rafi' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cVerily, merchants will be raised on the Day of Resurrection with the wicked, except for those who fear Allah, behave righteously, and are truthful.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1210 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0646 \u0631\u0627\u0641\u0639\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/even-smallest-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":12638,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Allah asks about even the smallest blessings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, among the blessing you will be questioned about on the Day of Resurrection are the cool shade, fresh dates, and cold water.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2369 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},